Transformation.Name: Field Recode
Transformation.SQLExpression: "N$10002" AS ( SELECT "BANK", "ACCOUNT", "ACCOUNT_ID", "AMOUNT", "TRANS_ID", "BALANCE", case when "TYPE" is null then 'Null bin' when "TYPE" IN ('PRIJEM') then '+1' when "TYPE" IN ('VYBER','VYDAJ') then '-1' else '<Other>' end "TYPE_BIN", case when "OPERATION" is null then 'Null bin' when "OPERATION" IN ('PREVOD NA UCET') then 'Remittance to another bank' when "OPERATION" IN ('PREVOD Z UCTU') then 'Collection from another bank' when "OPERATION" IN ('VKLAD') then 'Credit in cash' when "OPERATION" IN ('VYBER') then 'Withdrawal in cash' when "OPERATION" IN ('VYBER KARTOU') then 'Creadit card withdrawal' else 'Other' end "OPERATION_BIN", case when "K_SYMBOL" is null then 'Null bin' when "K_SYMBOL" IN ('DUCHOD') then 'Old-age pension' when "K_SYMBOL" IN ('POJISTNE') then 'Insurance payment' when "K_SYMBOL" IN ('SANKC. UROK') then 'Sanction interest' when "K_SYMBOL" IN ('SIPO') then 'Household' when "K_SYMBOL" IN ('SLUZBY') then 'Payment for statement' when "K_SYMBOL" IN ('UROK') then 'Interest credited' when "K_SYMBOL" IN ('UVER') then 'Loan payment' else '<Other>' end "K_SYMBOL_BIN",TO_DATE("TRX_DATE",'YYMMDD') - INTERVAL '100' YEAR(3) as "TRX_DT" FROM {INPUT_SOURCE} )

Transformation.Name: Trx Date Boundaries
Transformation.SQLExpression: "N$10006" AS ( SELECT "BANK", "ACCOUNT", "ACCOUNT_ID", "TRANS_ID", "BALANCE", "TYPE_BIN", "OPERATION_BIN", "K_SYMBOL_BIN", "TRX_DT", "TRX_AMOUNT",MIN("TRX_DT") OVER(PARTITION BY "ACCOUNT_ID" ) as "FIRST_TRX_DT",MAX("TRX_DT") OVER(PARTITION BY "ACCOUNT_ID" ) as "LAST_TRX_DT",COUNT(1) OVER(PARTITION BY "ACCOUNT_ID" ) as "TOT_TRX_CNT" FROM {INPUT_SOURCE} )
